</m:msup>
</m:mtd>
</m:mtr>
</m:mtable>
</m:math>
</para>
<para id="element-89">
The angular acceleration of the smaller wheel is :
</para>
<para id="element-90">
<m:math display="block">
<m:mtable columnalign="left">
<m:mtr>
<m:mtd>
<m:mo> ⇒ </m:mo> 
<m:msub>
<m:mi> α </m:mi>
<m:mn> 2 </m:mn>
</m:msub>
<m:mo> = </m:mo> 
